{
  "texts": [
    "Following the optimization of the reaction conditions using these 23 new ligands, the authors observed enhanced performance, surpassing that of previous reports (Figure 11).",
    "This study showcased how data science, ML algorithms, and reaction optimization can be used to discover reaction conditions that would have otherwise been overlooked by human intuition.",
    "Another great example of a combination of ML and AI cheminformatic tools and reaction optimization was reported by Nambiar et al. [84], who presented the use of a computer-aided synthesis planning (CASP) tool to find a threestep reaction pathway for the synthesis of the active pharmaceutical ingredient sonidegib (58).",
    "After the generation of multiple reaction pathways by the CASP tool, the authors manually selected a highly ranked route based on synthetic feasibility.",
    "This three-step reaction comprised an S N Ar, hydrogenative reduction of a nitro group, and an amide coupling (Table 2, entries 11 and 12)."
  ]
}